name: Corrupted Queen
description: Once a queen of a realm in a distant galaxy and responsible for its extinction. According to the legends, the corrupted queen seems to no longer follows a logical train of thought and have power to annihilate an entire planet. No one knows what triggered her revolt or if she is the real culprit for the murders. People just do their best not to be on the same planet as her, luckily she hasn't been seen for years.
